00:01:03.570 --> 00:01:05.290 align:middle line:90%
The psychic vampire.

00:01:05.290 --> 00:01:09.100 align:middle line:84%
The person, Howard, who
literally sucks the life out

00:01:09.100 --> 00:01:11.399 align:middle line:84%
