astonishing setting sun.

00:21:40.030 --> 00:21:41.950 align:middle line:84%
The whole city had
turned crimson.

00:21:41.950 --> 00:21:43.900 align:middle line:84%
And I ran up with
my digital camera

00:21:43.900 --> 00:21:46.912 align:middle line:84%
trying a dozen different
ways to capture it.

00:21:46.912 --> 00:21:48.620 align:middle line:84%
And this is the way
