And it's a reflection
of the tree above.

00:23:27.080 --> 00:23:30.020 align:middle line:84%
And every time it rains, when
you walk down the street,

00:23:30.020 --> 00:23:33.590 align:middle line:84%
you pass thousands of
these little microcosms.

00:23:33.590 --> 00:23:35.090 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And don't
even notice them.

